  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Interior Designer",
  "description": "<p>The ideal candidate will have excellent creative thinking skills and be able to create designs based on conversations with a client. The candidate should be confident communicating regularly with the client in order to assess their needs and be able to adjust a given approach based on feedback. The candidate should maintain familiarity with the interior design and trends in order to provide the best ideas for clients.</p>\n<p><br>\nJob Description &amp; Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Posses excellent design flair, efficient in AutoCad, 3D StudioMax, Photoshop skills to a high standard with an eye for details &amp; great personality</li>\n  <li>Design Conceptualization &amp; Space Management</li>\n  <li>With excellent communication &amp; presentation skills</li>\n  <li>Creative, able to think out of the box</li>\n  <li>Able to work under pressure/tight deadline</li>\n  <li>Strong in design concept &amp; detail drawings</li>\n  <li>Independent &amp; motivated</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of experience in commercial, retail &amp; hospitality design</li>\n</ul>",
